### Description of Issue
Hi,

If you have [sclo-sclo](http://mirror.centos.org/centos/7/sclo/x86_64/sclo/) repository enabled, when installing `salt-minion` from py3 repository it will take `sclo-cassandra3-zeromq-4.1.6-7.el7.x86_64` that is installed in /opt/rh/.... so not in path.
Salt-minion will not start.

Best regards,